  <summary date="2021-01-21T19:15:36Z" status="Introduced in House">Confronting the Threat of Domestic Terrorism Act

This bill applies penalties for international terrorism to certain domestic criminal offenses when they are committed with the intent to intimidate or coerce a civilian population, influence the policy of a government, or affect the conduct of a government.</summary>
